1194
01:27:56,720 --> 01:27:57,948
What's going on?

1195
01:27:58,080 --> 01:27:59,433
Get on stage.

1196
01:27:59,800 --> 01:28:01,711
-Where?
-On stage!

1197
01:28:02,160 --> 01:28:04,799
-Why? No! What am I going to do?
