Dewey!

1201
01:28:36,920 --> 01:28:37,989
Dewey!

1202
01:28:38,120 --> 01:28:39,394
Oh, my God!

1203
01:28:41,240 --> 01:28:42,355
Dewey!

1204
01:28:44,120 --> 01:28:45,678
Where's the band?

1205
01:28:46,080 --> 01:28:47,149
Dewey!

1206
01:28:47,480 --> 01:28:48,595
Dewey.

1207
01:28:48,720 --> 01:28:49,789
Dewey!

1208
01:28:52,040 --> 01:28:53,314
Dewey!

